ther hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/1113/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Lamotrigine, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, More', 'Dabrafenib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Ibrutinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, Brigatinib, More', 1767369485);
